data.description: Indulge in the perfect blend of sophistication and functionality with this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bath home, boasting an additional 4th room adaptable as an office or bedroom. Experience the allure of an open concept layout complemented by built-in surround sound for an immersive living experience.Rest easy with the added security provided by a home security system, while relishing the fresh appeal of newly painted interiors and the luxury of new LVP flooring in the master bedroom, bathroom, and closet. Embrace sustainability with leased solar and the convenience of a tankless water heater. Never worry about watering your yard again! This home comes equipped with a satellite irrigation system!This residence goes beyond the ordinary, offering a spacious 3-car garage for your convenience. Set in a prime location, it's a mere stroll away from Boris Elementary in the highly regarded Clovis Unified School District. Seize the opportunity to call this home yours, where modern elegance meets everyday practicality. Welcome to a life of refined comfort!
